Distilled California is the distiller-driven podcast for the booze nerd. Join hosts Dylan Almendral and Ryan Freisen as we take a deep dive into the bottle. We discuss the history, legends, politics and future of the California distilling industry from the ground up and distill what it means to be grain to glass in California. Ryan is a distiller and Vice President of the California Artisanal Distillers Guild. Dylan is a historian and writer. Both are devout students and stewards of the glass. This show exists to create informed drinkers. If you drink, know what's in your bottle! And, of course, to document the California distillery world while it is in its infancy. 
This podcast is for everyone; the aficionado, the vaguely interested, the distiller, the historian and the nerd alike. All are welcome and always will be. We all float down here. 

The podcast will feature tastings, science, history, interviews with distillers, book reviews, distributors, and of course, good times. 

Join us as we learn and pass on the experience to you!

I’m on a crazy journey to achieving my biggest life goal of living in 7 countries! Crazy?  Perhaps! I moved to New Zealand (country number 4), during the pandemic, with my husband, beautiful 4 year old daughter and our gorgeous black Labrador. 

I’m here to share my story, the ups and downs of my journey so far, the tips & tricks I have learnt along the way, and interviews with friends smashing out their own bucket lists, with the hope our stories and journeys can inspire you to make a plan to achieve your bucket lists whatever they may look like ... so all those “maybe one day” things become “I can’t believe I did it” things…

For me, the meaning of life is the collection of experiences we accumulate along the way and the incredible people we meet. Life is a journey, not a destination… it shouldn’t be about the “one day”, it should be about the everyday, about the experiences - so make the journey fun!

Yes you only live once, BUT you only die once, and you get the chance to live every single day!

So my question is… what’s stopping you from living the life you truly want and chasing YOUR bucket list dreams?

title: SHAMEFUL PROWESS Romance Super Novel June Release
description:
Charlee Rae grew up tucked away in a pauperized small town in Northern Mississippi. She spent her summers walking barefoot through old cotton mills and peeping over her pawpaw’s shoulder as he made moonshine in the foothills of the Appalachian Mountains.

Charlee knew at a young age that she had no desire to follow in the isolated footsteps of everyone in the deep South, especially those living in her sleepy town. She was born with ambition, determination, vitality, discipline and, above all, the natural looks and personality that set her apart from most of the world.

Trying to break away from the label of garbage can poor, Charlee’s charisma was inherent in her personality; however, her biggest fear was remaining on a route of strife and impoverishment. Due to this overwhelming fear, she grew up obsessed with the idea of opulence and finding ways to position herself among the social elite.

Charlee Rae’s targets were easily fooled by her charming character, which hid a cunning villainy. Charlee became the master of her fate, controlling people and circumstances that manufactured her dark side.

Charlee schooled herself on the established traits of being a master manipulator. She was uninhibited and iniquitous in using her appeal to lure in any man of her choice. However, these men always had one thing in common--money. Her endless games of trickery and implausible convictions fueled a thrilling rush but pushed her into a world of immorality.

Witness as Charlee Rae masters her craft of seduction to control the world’s richest and most powerful men. Fade into the emotional struggles of her upbringing that paved the path of her methodical thinking. Take a front-row seat to learn the bona fide secrets and wretchedness clung onto the crème de la crème. At what price would you sell your soul or commodify your body to the illusion of the haut monde? Suppose you were Charlee Rae, would you make the same risky decisions? Will authentic love finally end her compulsions?

5. Stories from the Road: Embark on virtual journeys through captivating narratives shared by fellow RV travelers. Experience the highs, the challenges, and the unforgettable moments that come with life on the road.

6. Expert Interviews: Benefit from in-depth conversations with industry professionals, travel bloggers, and seasoned adventurers. Gain expert advice on everything from route planning and boondocking to sustainable RVing practices and community engagement.

Join us as we unlock the secrets to a truly effortless RVing experience. Whether you're seeking inspiration for your next cross-country road trip or aiming to refine your RVing skills, Effortless RVing is here to guide you every mile of the way.
